From 9c9c99540d79ee101255d8c7fad772aa2ffef9c0 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: patch <patch@local>
Date: Tue, 7 Jul 2026 02:14:54 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: pare back Roles to beta (2 starter roles + custom,
 editable name/desc)

- Trim DEFAULT_ROLES to Efficient Haulers (merged station-hauler + courier
  weighting) and Bombers; custom roles and per-role weight overrides still
  work exactly as before.
- Add name/desc editing to RoleCard for both built-in and custom roles,
  persisted via RoleOverride.name/desc for built-ins and directly on
  CustomRoleDef for customs. Reset restores the original name too.
- Add a 'beta' badge next to the Roles nav item and on the Roles page
  heading; update intro copy to explain the smaller starter set.
